                    </span>
                </h4>
                <p>
                    A criminal background check typically reveals various types of information, including: - Felony and misdemeanor convictions - Arrest records - Pending criminal cases - Warrants - Sex offender registry status However, the extent of the information can vary based on state laws and the type of check conducted.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div>
