                    </span>
                </h4>
                <p>
                    Criminal background checks are crucial for employers to ensure workplace safety, protect company assets, and promote legal and compliant hiring practices. They help identify any potential criminal behavior that might pose risks to colleagues, clients, or the organization's reputation.
                </p>
