 34.8945C45.0198 32.7383 45.4885 30.4453 45.5002 28.0781C45.5119 25.6992 45.051 23.3906 44.1408 21.2188ZM38.2385 38.3281C35.5002 41.0391 31.8674 42.5312 28.0002 42.5312H27.9338C25.5783 42.5195 23.2385 41.9336 21.1721 40.832L20.844 40.6562H15.344V35.1562L15.1682 34.8281C14.0666 32.7617 13.4807 30.4219 13.469 28.0664C13.4533 24.1719 14.9416 20.5156 17.6721 17.7617C20.3987 15.0078 24.0432 13.4844 27.9377 13.4688H28.0041C29.9573 13.4688 31.8518 13.8477 33.6369 14.5977C35.3791 15.3281 36.9416 16.3789 38.2854 17.7227C39.6252 19.0625 40.6799 20.6289 41.4104 22.3711C42.1682 24.1758 42.5471 26.0898 42.5393 28.0664C42.5158 31.957 40.9885 35.6016 38.2385 38.3281Z" fill="#4F51FD"/></svg>
                    </span>
                </h4>
                <p>
                    The duration of a criminal background check can vary depending on the depth of the search and the agencies involved. Generally, it takes between one to five business days. Delays can occur due to factors like discrepancies in records or manual checks required by some state laws.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4>
                    <span>
                       <i>What are some common misconceptions about criminal background checks?</i>
                    </span>
                    <span>
                        <svg width="56" height="56" viewBox="0 0 56 56" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="56" height="56" rx="4" fill="#F2F3FF"/><path d="M26.1252 28C26.1252 28.4973 26.3228 28.9742 26.6744 29.3258C27.026 29.6775 27.5029 29.875 28.0002 29.875C28.4975 29.875 28.9744 29.6775 29.326 29.3258C29.6777 28.9742 29.8752 28.4973 29.8752 28C29.8752 27.5027 29.6777 27.0258 29.326 26.6742C28.9744 26.3225 28.4975 26.125 28.0002 26.125C27.5029 26.125 27.026 26.3225 26.6744 26.6742C26.3228 27.0258 26.1252 27.5027 26.1252 28ZM33.9377 28C33.9377 28.4973 34.1353 28.9742 34.4869 29.3258C34.8385 29.6775 35.3154 29.875 35.8127 29.875C36.31 29.875 36.7869 29.6775 37.1385 29.3258C37.4902 28.9742 37.6877 28.4973 37.6877 28C37.6877 27.5027 37.4902 27.0258 37.1385 26.6742C36.7869 26.3225 36.31 26.125 35.8127 26.125C35.3154 26.125 34.8385 26.3225 34.4869 26.6742C34.1353 27.0258 33.9377 27.5027 33.9377 28ZM18.3127 28C18.3127 28.4973 18.5103 28.9742 18.8619 29.3258C19.2135 29.6775 19.6904 29.875 20.1877 29.875C20.685 29.875 21.1619 29.6775 21.5135 29.3258C21.8652 28.9742 22.0627 28.4973 22.0627 28C22.0627 27.5027 21.8652 27.0258 21.5135 26.6742C21.1619 26.3225 20.685 26.125 20.1877 26.125C19.6904 26.125 19.2135 26.3225 18.8619 26.6742C18.5103 27.0258 18.3127 27.5027 18.3127 28ZM44.1408 21.2188C43.258 19.1211 41.9924 17.2383 40.3791 15.6211C38.7771 14.0133 36.8754 12.7352 34.7815 11.8594C32.633 10.957 30.3518 10.5 28.0002 10.5H27.9221C25.5549 10.5117 23.2619 10.9805 21.1057 11.9023C19.0297 12.7872 17.1458 14.0675 15.5588 15.6719C13.9612 17.2852 12.7073 19.1602 11.8401 21.25C10.9416 23.4141 10.4885 25.7148 10.5002 28.082C10.5135 30.7948 11.1553 33.4676 12.3752 35.8906V41.8281C12.3752 42.3047 12.5645 42.7617 12.9015 43.0987C13.2385 43.4357 13.6955 43.625 14.1721 43.625H20.1135C22.5365 44.845 25.2093 45.4867 27.9221 45.5H28.0041C30.344 45.5 32.6135 45.0469 34.7502 44.1602C36.8335 43.2947 38.7282 42.0316 40.3283 40.4414C41.9416 38.8438 43.2112 36.9766 44.0979 34.8945C45.0198 32.7383 45.4885 30.4453 45.5002 28.0781C45.5119 25.6992 45.051 23.3906 44.1408 21.2188ZM38.2385 38.3281C35.5002 41.0391 31.8674 42.5312 28.0002 42.5312H27.9338C25.5783 42.5195 23.2385 41.9336 21.1721 40.832L20.844 40.6562H15.344V35.1562L15.1682 34.8281C14.0666 32.7617 13.4807 30.4219 13.469 28.0664C13.4533 24.1719 14.9416 20.5156 17.6721 17.7617C20.3987 15.0078 24.0432 13.4844 27.9377 13.4688H28.0041C29.9573 13.4688 31.8518 13.8477 33.6369 14.5977C35.3791 15.3281 36.9416 16.3789 38.2854 17.7227C39.6252 19.0625 40.6799 20.6289 41.4104 22.3711C42.1682 24.1758 42.5471 26.0898 42.5393 28.0664C42.5158 31.957 40.9885 35.6016 38.2385 38.3281Z" fill="#4F51FD"/></svg>
                    </span>
                </h4>
                <p>
                    Common misconceptions include the belief that: - All criminal records are accessible; in reality, some may be sealed or expunged. - The checks reveal every detail about a person's past; they typically focus on criminal activity pertinent to the job. - Employers cannot hire someone with a record; however, relevance to the job and the time elapsed since the offense are considered.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4>
                    <span>
                       <i>Are criminal background checks legal?</i>
                    </span>
                    <span>
                        <svg width="56" height="56" viewBox="0 0 56 56" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="56" height="56" rx="4" fill="#F2F3FF"/><path d="M26.1252 28C26.1252 28.4973 26.3228 28.9742 26.6744 29.3258C27.026 29.6775 27.5029 29.875 28.0002 29.875C28.4975 29.875 28.9744 29.6775 29.326 29.3258C29.6777 28.9742 29.8752 28.4973 29.8752 28C29.8752 27.5027 29.6777 27.0258 29.326 26.6742C28.9744 26.3225 28.4975 26.125 28.0002 26.125C27.5029 26.125 27.026 26.3225 26.6744 26.6742C26.3228 27.0258 26.1252 27.5027 26.1252 28ZM33.9377 28C33.9377 28.4973 34.1353 28.9742 34.4869 29.3258C34.8385 29.6775 35.3154 29.875 35.8127 29.875C36.31 29.875 36.7869 29.6775 37.1385 29.3258C37.4902 28.9742 37.6877 28.4973 37.6877 28C37.6877 27.5027 37.4902 27.0258 37.1385 26.6742C36.7869 26.3225 36.31 26.125 35.8127 26.125C35.3154 26.125 34.8385 26.3225 34.4869 26.6742C34.1353 27.0258 33.9377 27.5027 33.9377 28ZM18.3127 28C18.3127 28.4973 18.5103 28.9742 18.8619 29.3258C19.2135 29.6775 19.6904 29.875 20.1877 29.875C20.685 29.875 21.1619 29.6775 21.5135 29.3258C21.8652 28.9742 22.0627 28.4973 22.0627 28C22.0627 27.5027 21.8652 27.0258 21.5135 26.6742C21.1619 26.3225 20.685 26.125 20.1877 26.125C19.6904 26.125 19.2135 26.3225 18.8619 26.6742C18.5103 27.0258 18.3127 27.5027 18.3127 28ZM44.1408 21.2188C43.258 19.1211 41.9924 17.2383 40.3791 15.6211C38.7771 14.0133 36.8754 12.7352 34.7815 11.8594C32.633 10.957 30.3518 10.5 28.0002 10.5H27.9221C25.5549 10.5117 23.2619 10.9805 21.1057 11.9023C19.0297 12.7872 17.1458 14.0675 15.5588 15.6719C13.9612 17.2852 12.7073 19.1602 11.8401 21.25C10.9416 23.4141 10.4885 25.7148 10.5002 28.082C10.5135 30.7948 11.1553 33.4676 12.3752 35.8906V41.8281C12.3752 42.3047 12.5645 42.7617 12.9015 43.0987C13.2385 43.4357 13.6955 43.625 14.1721 43.625H20.1135C22.5365 44.845 25.2093 45.4867 27.9221 45.5H28.0041C30.344 45.5 32.6135 45.0469 34.7502 44.1602C36.8335 43.2947 38.7282 42.0316 40.3283 40.4414C41.9416 38.8438 43.2112 36.9766 44.0979 34.8945C45.0198 32.7383 45.4885 30.4453 45.5002 28.0781C45.5119 25.6992 45.051 23.3906 44.1408 21.2188ZM38.2385 38.3281C35.5002 41.0391 31.8674 42.5312 28.0002 42.5312H27.9338C25.5783 42.5195 23.2385 41.9336 21.1721 40.832L20.844 40.6562H15.344V35.1562L15.1682 34.8281C14.0666 32.7617 13.4807 30.4219 13.469 28.0664C13.4533 24.1719 14.9416 20.5156 17.6721 17.7617C20.3987 15.0078 24.0432 13.4844 27.9377 13.4688H28.0041C29.9573 13.4688 31.8518 13.8477 33.6369 14.5977C35.3791 15.3281 36.9416 16.3789 38.2854 17.7227C39.6252 19.0625 40.6799 20.6289 41.4104 22.3711C42.1682 24.1758 42.5471 26.0898 42.5393 28.0664C42.5158 31.957 40.9885 35.6016 38.2385 38.3281Z" fill="#4F51FD"/></svg>
                    </span>
                </h4>
                <p>
                    Yes, criminal background checks are legal, though they must comply with federal laws such as the Fair Credit Reporting Act (FCRA) and any relevant state regulations. Employers must also ensure they follow equal employment opportunity laws to avoid discrimination.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4>
                    <span>
