                    </span>
                    <span>
                        <svg width="56" height="56" viewBox="0 0 56 56" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="56" height="56" rx="4" fill="#F2F3FF"/><path d="M26.1252 28C26.1252 28.4973 26.3228 28.9742 26.6744 29.3258C27.026 29.6775 27.5029 29.875 28.0002 29.875C28.4975 29.875 28.9744 29.6775 29.326 29.3258C29.6777 28.9742 29.8752 28.4973 29.8752 28C29.8752 27.5027 29.6777 27.0258 29.326 26.6742C28.9744 26.3225 28.4975 26.125 28.0002 26.125C27.5029 26.125 27.026 26.3225 26.6744 26.6742C26.3228 27.0258 26.1252 27.5027 26.1252 28ZM33.9377 28C33.9377 28.4973 34.1353 28.9742 34.4869 29.3258C34.8385 29.6775 35.3154 29.875 35.8127 29.875C36.31 29.875 36.7869 29.6775 37.1385 29.3258C37.4902 28.9742 37.6877 28.4973 37.6877 28C37.6877 27.5027 37.4902 27.0258 37.1385 26.6742C36.7869 26.3225 36.31 26.125 35.8127 26.125C35.3154 26.125 34.8385 26.3225 34.4869 26.6742C34.1353 27.0258 33.9377 27.5027 33.9377 28ZM18.3127 28C18.3127 28.4973 18.5103 28.9742 18.8619 29.3258C19.2135 29.6775 19.6904 29.875 20.1877 29.875C20.685 29.875 21.1619 29.6775 21.5135 29.3258C21.8652 28.9742 22.0627 28.4973 22.0627 28C22.0627 27.5027 21.8652 27.0258 21.5135 26.6742C21.1619 26.3225 20.685 26.125 20.1877 26.125C19.6904 26.125 19.2135 26.3225 18.8619 26.6742C18.5103 27.0258 18.3127 27.5027 18.3127 28ZM44.1408 21.2188C43.258 19.1211 41.9924 17.2383 40.3791 15.6211C38.7771 14.0133 36.8754 12.7352 34.7815 11.8594C32.633 10.957 30.3518 10.5 28.0002 10.5H27.9221C25.5549 10.5117 23.2619 10.9805 21.1057 11.9023C19.0297 12.7872 17.1458 14.0675 15.5588 15.6719C13.9612 17.2852 12.7073 19.1602 11.8401 21.25C10.9416 23.4141 10.4885 25.7148 10.5002 28.082C10.5135 30.7948 11.1553 33.4676 12.3752 35.8906V41.8281C12.3752 42.3047 12.5645 42.7617 12.9015 43.0987C13.2385 43.4357 13.6955 43.625 14.1721 43.625H20.1135C22.5365 44.845 25.2093 45.4867 27.9221 45.5H28.0041C30.344 45.5 32.6135 45.0469 34.7502 44.1602C36.8335 43.2947 38.7282 42.0316 40.3283 40.4414C41.9416 38.8438 43.2112 36.9766 44.0979