                    </span>
                </h4>
                <p>
                    Applicants can prepare by being honest about their past if asked, checking their own criminal history to understand what might appear, and reviewing relevant laws to know their rights. Being upfront allows candidates to explain past issues directly with potential employers.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4>
