                </h4>
                <p>
                    To ensure workplace safety, employers can:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Conduct regular risk assessments to identify potential hazards.</li>
                    <li>Provide comprehensive safety training for all employees.</li>
                    <li>Implement appropriate safety protocols and emergency procedures.</li>
                    <li>Maintain equipment properly and ensure it's safe to use.</li>
                    <li>Encourage open communication for reporting hazards without fear of retribution.</li>
                </ul>
